"><div style="text-align:center"><font color="#77c145"><span style="font-size:18px"><strong>Lustrum Commissie</strong></span></font></div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnCaptionBlock" style="border-collapse:collapse"><tbody class="mcnCaptionBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnCaptionBlockInner" valign="top" style="padding:9px"><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="mcnCaptionRightContentOuter" width="100%" style="border-collapse:collapse"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" class="mcnCaptionRightContentInner" style="padding:0 9px"><table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="mcnCaptionRightImageContentContainer" width="175" style="border-collapse:collapse; float:left"><tbody><tr><td class="mcnCaptionRightImageContent" align="left" valign="top" style=""><img alt="" src="https://mcusercontent.com/74d4087b42fdc0ae42c3d27e2/_compresseds/bc219333-40af-3d0b-b6fb-0984849d2066.jpg" width="175" class="mcnImage" style="max-width:3508px; border:0; height:auto; outline:none; text-decoration:none; vertical-align:bottom"> </td></tr></tbody></table><table class="mcnCaptionRightTextContentContainer" align="right" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="352" style="border-collapse:collapse; float:right"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" class="mcnTextContent" style="word-break:break-word; color:#202020; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14px; line-height:150%; text-align:left"><p style="margin:10px 0; padding:0; color:#202020; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14px; line-height:150%; text-align:left">Ja, ja, het is bijna zover: volgend jaar viert S.V. Syntaxis haar 9e lustrum!</p><p style="margin:10px 0; padding:0; color:#202020; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14px; line-height:150%; text-align:left">Elke vijf jaar staan we stil bij hoe onze vereniging is gegroeid en vieren we dit met een speciaal lustrumjaar. Dit keer vieren we ons 45-jarig jubileum met een jaar vol feesten, herinneringen en bijzondere activiteiten!</p><p style="margin:10px 0; padding:0; color:#202020; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14px; line-height:150%; text-align:left">Lijkt het jou leuk om mee te helpen met het bedenken en&nbsp;organiseren van deze toffe feesten en unieke evenementen? Dan is dit jouw kans!</p><p style="margin:10px 0; padding:0; color:#202020; font-family:Helvetica; font-size:14px; line-height:150%; text-align:left">Schrijf je snel in via <a href="https://syntaxis.us14.list-manage.com/track/click?u=74d4087b42fdc0ae42c3d27e2&amp;id=3d4968ca9d&amp;e=0728742cd7" rel="noopener" target="_blank" style="color:#007C89; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline"><span style="color:#77c145">syntaxis.nl/lustrum</span></a>&nbsp;of stuur een mail naar <a href="mailto:intern@syntaxis.nl" target="_blank" style="color:#007C89; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline"><span style="color:#77c145">intern@syntaxis.nl</span></a>&nbsp;en maak deel uit van deze bijzondere viering!</p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnDividerBlock" style="min-width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; table-layout:fixed!important"><tbody class="mcnDividerBlockOuter"><tr><td class="mcnDividerBlockInner" style="min-width:100%; padding:18px"><table class="mcnDividerContent" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="min-width:100%; border-top:2px solid #77C145; border-collapse:collapse"><tbody><tr><td style=""><span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnTextBlock" style="min-width:100%; border-collapse:collapse"><tbody class="mcnTextBlockOuter"><tr><td valign="top" class="mcnTextBlockInner" style="padding-top:9px"><table align="left" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" class="mcnTextContentContainer" style="max-width:100%